@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_crcbdp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.39)) / wp.sin((tmp + 0.02 / v1 + 0.78)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.43 / v2 + 0.50) - 0.34))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((tmp + 0.50 * v2 + 0.85)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v0 + (tmp + 0.46 / v0 + 0.50)))
    tmp = 0.42
    v1 = wp.abs(0.46)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.55 * tmp + 0.14)) + ((v0 + 0.27 - tmp + 0.16) + (v1 + 0.34 * v1 + 0.31)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.95) / v0)
    data[tid] = v0
